description: Love that licorice life? Emerald Sky’s Indica Grape Noir Licorice Sticks are locally-sourced and delightfully potent. Made from vegan, organic ingredients, these indica candies are just as good for your body as they are for your soul. Hailing from the Bay Area, Emerald Sky is committed to the highest quality cannabis and the smoothest THC flavor. Each licorice is individually packaged to make sure you get the perfect dose every single time. Discreet and delicious––what’s not to love?

Emerald Sky’s Alpine Strawberry Sativa Licorice is the easiest way to stimulate your mind. You can’t taste the sativa, but you can certainly feel it as it boosts your focus and charges your social energy. These licorice strips are individually packaged to ensure you get just the right dose and just the right high. Made of vegan, organic, locally-sourced ingredients, these discrete candies are soothing for your body and mind.

ISLAND is the most laid back producer of responsible artisanal  cannabis. They’re all about keeping things fresh, natural, and locally sourced. Their Blackberry OG is one of their most popular Indicas, for staying in and zoning out. It’s sweet and smooth and smells like berries, what’s not to love? Relax your body, unwind your mind, drift off to sleep––ISLAND Blackberry OG’s got your back.

Set this one aside for your next binge watching session. Glass House Farms’ Hellfire OG is just as powerful as it sounds. It’ll melt every single inch of your body into the couch, so have your snacks ready in advance. You probably won’t get much done, but you will take off to a delightful daydream. Glass House Farms is a leader in craft cannabis, with intentionally-cultivated, sun-powered cannabis products you can count on.

We love the good folk at ISLAND, because they oh so carefully curate their line of cannabis products. 100% natural, 100% locally-sourced, their Mango Haze is a perfect reflection of their commitment to quality. Inspiring warm summer vibes, this sweet sativa packs an exotic fruit punch into your next best high. It’s smooth, cerebral, and sumptuous, inducing good times out and getting things done.

Named North America’s Bestselling Brand by Leaflink, Pacific Stone is without a doubt a fan favorite. Their Hybrid 805 Glue flower is one of their most popular strains for its potency and euphoria-inducing properties. It’s ultra relaxing and ultra top-shelf, with an earthy, sour finish. For a hybrid that moves with you, Pacific Stone’s 805 Glue is a versatile, go-to choice.

Pacific Stone has been named the Best Selling Brand in North America by Leaflink, and its Hybrid Glue Flower Pouch is one of its heaviest hitters. Known all across SoCal for its potency and earthy, sour flavor, this go-to hybrid might as well be a staple in every stash. One hit, and you’ll be transported to deep states of relaxation and euphoria. Give this top-shelf favorite a try!

Pacific Stone promises a smile in every bowl, and their Sativa Banjo delivers just that. This bright and beaming sativa revs you up with the scent of freshly picked oranges and lemons, so you can focus better and bust through those creative blocks. Wonderfully cerebral, delightfully earthy, this is the perfect choice for socializing or setting out on your next big project.

Pacific Stone was named North America’s Bestselling Brand, and their Banjo flower proves why. Crafted with your happiness in mind, this freshness-sealed pouch delivers 28.0g of euphoria-inducing flower to smoke and share. With Pacfic Stone, there’s a smile packed into every bowl. Uplift, relax, rejoice, and unwind with some of the most premium and potent flower on the market.

They call it Private Reserve Og for a reason. It’s their creme de la creme. Their chef d'oeuvre. This flower masterpiece is as top shelf as it gets. Ultra premium. Ultra potent. For an Indica that takes over your entire body, leaving you fully and completely relaxed, this is the only choice. Unwind with the finest.

Space Coyote is the out-of-this-world cannabis curator that delivers smokable, potent products with artistry and delight. Their Indica Hash Joint ranks among their flagship products, and we know you’ll fall head over heels for it. Made of nothing less than mind-melting indica, these prerolls will whisk you away. Take off to a tropical vacation in your body and mind without having to grind, roll, or pack.

Space Coyote is a brand that’s just as fun as it sounds. Their out-of-this-world Sativa Hash Joint sets out to “not suck,” and boy, does it do that. Bursting with good vibes and rich flavors, this hash-infused preroll wakes you up. Take a puff, become your best, most joyful self, then pass it on to a friend. There’s no better companion to good times and good people then the craft collabs from Space Coyote.

Let ‘s be real: fresh coffee and donuts is one of the most sumptuous ways to get your day going right. Coda’s signature cannabis-infused chocolate bar aims to evoke that same sensation. Producing an uplifting, healing high, one bite of this rich chocolate edible will get you ready-to-go, but not in a rush. The lush flavor of South American milk chocolate is rounded out with notes of coffee, cinnamon sugar, and toasted milk. Coda’s Signature Chocolate Coffee & Donuts chocolate bar has been recognized by the High Times Cannabis Cup and Colorado LeafLink List two years in a row. Get it here.

The comfort of cheesecake and the milky flavor of Ecuadorian white chocolate rolled into one 100% decadent, 100% delightful cannabis-infused chocolate bar. With notes of sour cream, lemon, crumble and spice, Coda’s Signature Chocolate Cream & Crumble is just as sumptuous as it is effective. Coda Signature’s edible collection fuses classical French culinary techniques with organic chemistry and industrial design to create whimsical edibles that taste and feel just right.

Maple and pecan delight the senses while cannabis inspires the mind in this ethically-sourced chocolate bar. It’s sweet and smooth and smokey, with depths of flavor and exactly the potency you’re looking for. Recognized by the THC Championship, this award-winning chocolate bar wakes up the mind, while relaxing the body. Coda Signature’s line of cannabis-infused chocolate bars represent French culinary technique, industrial design, and organic chemistry. Their Maple & Pecan chocolate bar is one of their most delightful experiments––give it a try!

Sativa that’s cool and frosty and never ceases to Deliver. Pacific Stone’s Banjo Sativa Pouch is uplifting and powerfully cerebral. Earthy, citrus notes stimulate your senses while boosting your creativity and focus. Recognized as North America’s Best Selling Brand, Pacific Stone’s flower collection has freshness sealed in and is intended to be packed, smoked, and shared.

Pacific Stone produces their flower with the intention of a smile in every bowl. The time and care they put into their customers’ happiness earned them a rightful recognition as North America’s Best Selling Brand. Their Hybrid 805 Glue Pouch is a fan favorite for its potency and versatility. For a trip to euphoria, there’s no substitute.

F/ELD is based out of sunny California, and their Golden State Banana concentrate is an ode to their home state. This hybrid is as laid back as an afternoon by the Santa Monica docks and as breezy as a hike through the Hollywood Hills. F/ELD’s full spectrum cannabis concentrates merge science with passion into one unbeatable cannabis brand. Give it a try for yourself.

Humboldt Terp Council’s Gasolina Sauce is the love-child of OG Kush and Sour Diesel, meaning it goes down smooth with a hint of tartness. This live resin creates a warm, healing pressure around the crown of your head, helping to ease your mind and reduce tension. It’s long lasting, pain relieving, and seriously potent Note: you’ll want to pace yourself with this one ;) Humboldt Terp Council is a NorCal based cultivator that obsesses over the details. Give their spellbinding Live Resin a try.

Spotlight on: Pacific Stone––North America’s Best Selling Brand, according to Leaflink. Brighten up your mood with their Hybrid 805 Sour Pouch. Make the most of your high with this robust flower that seeps into your body and your mind for an overall chill that suits every occasion. Classic, tangy, and a customer favorite!

We believe Pacific Stone delivers some of the absolute best indoor greenhouse flower in sunny California, and we’re not alone. Recognized as the Best Selling Brand in North America by Leaflink, Pacific stone’s flower pouches are known throughout the industry as a customer favorite. Their Indica Wedding Cake Flower Pouch is sweet and sedative, producing a powerful body high that will whisk you off to your deepest state of relaxation. It’s time to truly chill.

Sweet and decadent, Pacific Stone’s Indica Wedding Cake Flower lulls you into a state of pure relaxation. The perfect choice for getting to know your couch a little better, this ultra calming, borderline sedative, indica will carry away all the stress within your body and mind. Frosty, flavorful, and famously potent, Pacific Stone’s Indica Wedding Cake is your new best friend for staying in.

Put the lime in the coconut and drink it all up. Put the lime in the coconut and…add some cannabis to it? Yes! Coda Fruit’s Coconut & Lime Gummies are tangy with a twist of the exotic. Intended to energize and uplift, these gummies promise the sheer bliss of a seaside afternoon. Sail away to somewhere sweet with these culinary-inspired cannabis treats.

Imagine the first day of summer in one cannabis-infused bite. Coda’s Strawberry & Rhubarb gummies are inspired by seaside afternoons and balmy nights. Summer strawberry is paired with tart rhubarb for a sweet and tangy twist that’s sure to delight your senses. With a 1:1 CBD to THC ratio, these gummies guarantee an even, balanced high that soothes the body and mind. Dusted with vanilla bean sugar for just a little extra magic, it’s no surprise these gummies were recognized by the THC Championship two years in a row.

Love a spicy margarita? You’ll adore Coda’s Pineapple & Jalapeno gummies. Blending sweetness with a big, big bite, these gummies heat you up, then cool you down. The 1:2 CBD to TCH ratio ensures you’ll chill out completely while buzzing with energy. For anyone who’s ever needed an extra kick, these gummies are for you.

Live resin is Humboldt Terp Council’s flagship product for a reason. Extracted from fresh frozen flowers, their cannabis products are known across the industry as “the champagne of concentrates.” Their Hybrid Peach resin sauce is inspired by sweet and juicy peach rings: full of luxurious flavor, with soft, earthy undertones.

Go with the masses, and get your taste of one of Leaflink’s Bestselling Brands in North America. Pacific Stone is a fan favorite for indoor greenhouse flower. Grown under the California sun, their Hybrid 805 Glue is as warm and vibrant as a beachside afternoon. This unique strain builds you up, while calming you down, ensuring the perfect balance between head and body high. No grinding or packing necessary with these convenient prerolls. Pass them around or keep ‘em for yourself. You’ll love the high either way.

F/ELD is a Los Angeles-based manufacturer of cannabis products, best known for their award-winning Live Resins. Their Lemon Chem is one of their bestsellers, and for good reason. Good thing we found this lemon-inspired extraction for you.

Say hello to F/Eld Extracts, the developers of their ultra premium, ultra potent Live Resin. These unbeatable concentrates are made without solvents or additives to ensure all of the power with none of the impurities. Los Angeles-based F/ELD designed their extracts with unique cannabinoids to help relieve chronic pain while stimulating the body and mind. They’ve won awards for their solvent-free products, and their Docs OG will quickly show you why.

F/ELD concentrates are award-winningly good. Their Tar Hill Pink Lemonade represents the F/ELD’s team commitment to quality and craftsmanship in every strain they concoct. It’s sweet and tangy and creates a versatile high that fits your every mood. When you want to elevate your mind, while relaxing your body, this is the go-to choice.

If you can’t sit still, then F/ELD’s Disposable Mini Pens are for you. They’re discreet, portable, and get the job done. F/ELD’s award-winning cannabis team has perfected ultra potent, ultra pure concentrates that are full of flavor and full of fun. The best part? You can vape confidently, knowing there’s no extra additives or terpenes. This Larry Pie disposable pen will lift your spirits and take you to greener pastures.

Take off to another dimension of bliss with PLUS’s Uplift Sour Watermelon Gummies. These fruit-forward, playful bites uplift your mind and soul for hours at a time. Sweet on the tongue with a lingering sour finish––the perfect accompaniment to a sunshine afternoon. For a refreshing way to amplify your day, these gummies hit the spot.

We love a hybrid THC/CBD edible for its healing properties. THC elevates your mood, while CBD relaxes every muscle in your body. These blueberry bites are the perfect blend of sweet and sour and provide the relief you need from everyday stress. PLUS is a progressively-minded, California-based cannabis producer. You’ll love getting to know them.

You like to feel good, and the fine folks at PLUS want you to feel good too. That’s why they concocted their Concord Grape THC/CBD hybrid gummies that are sweet, juicy, and remarkably relaxing. The perfect nighttime companion, these grape bites unleash your calmest, most peaceful self. The THC to CBD ratio ensures you unwind your body, without winding up your mind. Release the Zen in you.

Just a whiff of fresh tangerines and your senses are elevated to the next level. The super progressive, super Cali team at PLUS developed these uplifting gummies with that exact sensation in mind. These tangy, sour bites wake up your mind and body with a wash of pure euphoria. When you want to see the world in a brighter, clearer way, these gummies are your vehicle. Get a little more out of your day.

Like sitting under a lemon tree on a sunny afternoon, Pacific Stone’s Sativa Lemon Prerolls are refreshing, vibrant, and fill you with life. The citrus aroma awakens the senses, increasing focus and alertness. Ideal for bright, beaming days full of friends or just getting things done. Pacfic Stone was named one of Leaflink’s Bestselling Brands, and their Lemon Sativa is a great example of why. Elevate your mind the sweet way.

Your day is full of ups and downs, but PLUS’s Black Cherry Unwind Mints are always the same––calming, cooling, and full of flavor. They’re rich and sweet and just the right amount of tart. When things wind up, they wind you down. Get your peace of mind in just one bite.

The future of cannabis is here with F/ELD’s high tech, yet simple to use mini and disposable Vape Sauce Pens. These little guys exemplify the notion of “small but mighty,” because they pack so much flavor and potency into one pocket-sized pen. Enjoy .4g of F/ELD’s additive-free Kosher Kush concentrate wherever your day takes you.

Discrete, portable, and packed with flavor, this mini pen is the perfect cannabis solution on-the-go. 100% Distillate Free, with no added terpenes or additives––treat yourself to the good stuff.

There’s nothing cuter than a mini. This miniature version of F/ELD’s signature Sauce Pen is a .4 gram disposable vaporizer. Based in sunny Los Angeles, F/ELD single handedly devised this vaporizer with a unique ceramic heating device. Known for their award-winning concentrates, the 100% distillate free blend of full spectrum high terpene and cannabinoid extract will win you over in an instant.

Hybrid flower has a little to offer everyone. Sativa to lift you up, then indica to relax you back down. Glass House’s Marsmalade does just that, with a sweet and earthy flavor that tastes just right. You determine the journey you want to go on, with this versatile flower that bends to your every whim. Heavy, floaty, you name the sensation, and it moves with you. Our go-to for a warm summer night with good food and good company.

We adore the cannabis producers at ISLAND, because they handcraft their products with ‘lots and ‘lots of love. Experience Leaflink’s Bestselling Brand in a convenient preroll. Sativas are social, and so are these portable little guys that are perfect for puffing and passing. Pacific Stone’s Lemon Sativa is vibrant, energizing, and cerebral. It boosts your brainwaves to inspire clearer creativity and communication. Take off to another level of clarity with these citrusy sweet prerolls.

Discover why Pacific Stone was named Leaflink’s Bestselling Brand in North America. Their Private Reserve Indica Prerolls are the perfect place to start. Light one up, and get ready for a warm wave to wash over you, as your mind and body unwinds to another dimension. For another level of relaxation, this is the top shelf choice.

Now’s the time to create a peaceful state for yourself. Let PLUS Tropical Mango Relief Gummies help relieve you of all the cares of the day. These juicy mango bites are rich in CBD to create the most relaxing possible body sensation, without too much going on in your head. Combat stress, muscle tension, and your every ache and pain with these chiller-than-chill gummies.

Atlas’s line of delicious and wholesome edibles are developed to provide the most balanced, healing high. Blending creativity-enhancing sativas with a hint of relaxing indica ensures an even effect that never overwhelms. For a sweet treat that cuts the edge off, these are the perfect bite sized snacks.

Dark chocolate, pecan, and hazelnut fuse together in these delicious granola clusters that take you to another dimension of playfulness, mindfulness, and balance. Atlas is a small craft brand, and this indica-forward edible is one of their most popular products. With hints of cinnamon and salt, you’ll hit that sweet and salty spot while unleashing your creative spirit. Snack your way to your most Zen self.

With each serving individually wrapped, you can ensure the correct dosing every single time. While you can’t taste the THC, you can certainly feel it sinking into your skin and relaxing your body from head to toe. Kick back with an indica edible that’s sure to delight.

Coated in chocolate, filled with yummy, yummy peanut butter, and infused with tasteless, yet potent Sativa THC, these bite-sized treats are sure to satisfy your body and mind. This gentle, earthy CBD flower relaxes your body while keeping your mind on Earth. Take a hit, sit back, and let a wave of calm wash over you. This is the perfect solution for anyone looking to reduce anxiety, cigarette dependence, or body aches. New to cannabis? This is a low key way to ease in!

Chemistry is a craft curator of full-spectrum cannabis products that are 100% additive free. Get the refresh you deserve.

itemname: Ice Cream Cake by Mindfulness Farms
description: Based out of California’s Emerald Triangle, Flow Kana’s products are just as vibrant and iconic as the region they come from. Their Ice Cream Cake cannabis strain takes you on a journey. From buzzed and social to relaxed and aimless, it’ll carry you from socializing with friends to cozying up on the couch. Sweet and decadent, like a slice of ice cream cake, this indica hybrid is the perfect way to flow through your day.

The Flow Kana team seeks out craft cannabis farmers all over Northern California to curate a line of cannabis products that are as delightful as they are socially-responsible. Their Orange Creamsicle by Sol Grow blends the rich creaminess of vanilla with a sharp twist of citrus for a slightly warming, slightly tangy twist on your favorite kind of flower. This sativa-forward hybrid lifts you up with euphoria and bliss. Perfect for a sun shining afternoon.

We love Flow Kana, because they support farmers across Northern California. They seek out the best of the best in family-run, small-batch cannabis production and make their products available to the world. Their 13 Jacks collab with Whitethorn Valley Form is an energizing sativa that builds you up, and let’s you soar. Socialize, get creative, or just chill out with this sungrown craft cannabis.

itemname: Blue City Diesel by Elkhorn Ranch
description: What’s great about Flow Kana? They source their cannabis from small batch family-run farmers across Northern California. That means, they care about the local economy, just as much as they care about the quality of their products. Their socially-responsible Blue City Diesel by Elkhorn Ranch collab with Moon Made Farms in Humboldt County is sweet and floral and allows your mind wander. This indica-forward hybrid is perfect for a chill afternoon with your favorite project, whether that’s painting, walking along the lake, or baking up some lemon scones. Perk up your curiosity, then go with the flow.

itemname: Thunder Bucket Face Punch by HappyDay Farm
description: The team at Flow Kana is driven by their powerful mission to support local, family-run farms, while delivering expertly-crafted, small batch cannabis products. This indica hybrid is a fan favorite for unleashing all of the cares of the world in one clean, easy preroll.

Hang at a bar, bake a cake, write the next great American novel––Cosmic Dream will guide you where you need to go.
